FBIS3-58370 "drweu008_a_94001" FBIS-WEU-94-008 Document Type:Daily Report 12 Jan 1994 AUSTRIA Mock Comments on Zhirinovskiy's Importance AU1101121294 Vienna KURIER in German 11 Jan 94 p 2 AU1101121294 Vienna KURIER Language: German Article Type:BFN [Unattributed report: "Vladimir Outside the Door"] [Text] One should not "promote" Valdimir Zhirinovskiy "to most important man in the world," Foreign Minister Mock says. Spectacular refusals to grant him a visa just give the Russian nationalist leader greater weight. The decision to grant him a visa should be made on a case-by-case basis, Mock says.
